---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>AI, API & Integration Governance</h2>
		<p>Define practical governance models for APIs, integrations, AI-enabled services and shared platform capabilities.</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Clarify which APIs, integrations and data capabilities matter most for your business.</li>
			<li>Establish governance for lifecycle management, reuse, ownership and quality.</li>
			<li>Align integration and API decisions with enterprise architecture and target architecture principles.</li>
			<li>Create scalable operating models across teams, vendors and platforms.</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="strategy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>AI-Driven Product & Platform Strategy</h2>
		<p>Design platform and product strategies that combine APIs, integrations, AI and data into reusable business capabilities and scalable customer value.</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Define platform product vision aligned with business strategy and target architecture.</li>
			<li>Identify where AI-enabled features, automation and data capabilities create real customer value.</li>
			<li>Shape reusable APIs and platform capabilities teams and partners can build on.</li>
			<li>Align product roadmaps, architecture and governance around measurable outcomes.</li>
			<li>Support platform and product leaders in prioritising transformation initiatives.</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="heart" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Architecture Renewal & Modernisation</h2>
		<p>Modernise legacy integration and platform architectures toward scalable, API-first and AI-ready environments.</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Renew fragmented integration landscapes and outdated delivery models.</li>
			<li>Use AI-assisted analysis and agents to accelerate legacy system understanding.</li>
			<li>Design integration architectures aligned with strategic architecture principles and target architecture.</li>
			<li>Improve scalability, reuse and governance without slowing delivery.</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="pencil-line" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Operating Models & Delivery Enablement</h2>
		<p>Improve collaboration between architecture, platform, product and delivery teams.</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Design practical cross-team ways of working.</li>
			<li>Connect delivery practices with architecture and integration goals.</li>
			<li>Facilitate workshops, retrospectives and transformation initiatives.</li>
			<li>Help organisations evolve ways of working without unnecessary process overhead.</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: var(--rounded-sm);
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	.skills ul {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.5rem;
		padding-left: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--gray-300);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: var(--rounded-sm);
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
			gap: 3rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
